subject: Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show
Photography
Dogs
lead_paragraph: John Ashbey, equipped with squeaky toys shaped like carrots and a noisy Nemo toy, makes every effort to get the perfect posed shot of Westminster’s top dogs.
